<p class="">The Attorney-General has entirely confirmed everything that I was saying. All I said was that it is perfectly plain that some kind of complaint must have come to the Government. I was saying—and the Attorney-General has confirmed it—that there was no matter of wide or urgent public importance; that nobody had any idea what the allegations were; and that there was no public concern.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
