        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-a6b24da6-ec91-43e0-b663-ca02953e2dfb">
                The Lord President of the Council (Mr. Herbert Morrison)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-a6b24da6-ec91-43e0-b663-ca02953e2dfb" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1949-02-03/debates/63086899-ed69-4e51-9159-f7bab97b8c20/MinistersAndPublicServants(OfficialConduct)#contribution-a6b24da6-ec91-43e0-b663-ca02953e2dfb">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">It is only fair to the Tribunal to say that they absolutely cleared my hon. Friend the Member for Sowerby (Mr. Belcher) in the particular case to which my hon. Friend the Member for King's Norton (Mr. Blackburn) has referred.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
