<p class="">Will my right hon. and learned Friend permit me—</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-af48d0c7-7aa7-4d22-ac7f-0f2e83eeb1a2" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
