                Colonel Dower  (Penrith and Cockermouth)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-77590519-7c06-4a8c-a22e-46a27a8afc24" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
